The paper is about improving the reranking method for image search using Bag-of-Words (BoW) and image graph. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of rank-level feature fusion, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a method for encoding relevance among images, which involves graph theory and optimization, making it relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as well.
